    <!-- BEGIN OUTER-LEFT -->
<div id="outer-left">
        <div id="node-961" class="node clear-block">
        <div class="content">
 	    <h3 class="pgtitle">Special Collections and Archives</h3> 
        <span class='print-link'></span><p>The Special Collections and Archives houses some of the more unique, rare and valuable collections in the Brock University Library. Our primary collecting interests include:<br />&bull;	<a href="https://brocku.ca/library/collections/special-collections-archives/niagara">The Niagara Collection</a><br />&bull;	<a href="https://brocku.ca/library/collections/special-collections-archives/autism-collection">The Autism Collection</a> <br />&bull;	<a href="https://brocku.ca/library/collections/special-collections-archives/loyalists">The Loyalist Collection</a><br />&bull;	<a href="https://brocku.ca/library/collections/special-collections-archives/masonic-book-collection">The Masonic Book Collection</a><br />&bull;	<a href="http://brocku.v1.libguides.com/warof1812">War of 1812 materials</a><br />&bull;	<a href="http://dr.library.brocku.ca/handle/10464/9">University Archives</a> <br />&bull;	Rare books</p>
<p>The department is located on the 10th floor of the James A. Gibson Library in the Schmon Tower.</p>
<p style="padding-top: 5px !important; padding-right: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 5px !important; padding-left: 0px !important; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Descriptions of most items in the Special Collections and Archives can be found in the Library Catalogue.&nbsp;<a style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; " href="http://catalogue.library.brocku.ca/search/X?SEARCH=&amp;SORT=D&amp;b=spcl%20&amp;b=arch">Click here for a Special Collections and Archives' search.</a></p>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">
<div style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; "><strong>Hours:</strong></div>
<div style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; ">Monday to Friday: 9:30 a.m. - 4:30 p.m.&nbsp;</div>
<div style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; ">Saturday and Sunday: Closed.</div>
<div style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; "><em>*Appointments are recommended.*</em></div>
<div style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; ">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><strong>Basic Rules:</strong></div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">
<div>&bull; &nbsp;Fill out a visitor form upon arriving in the Special Collections</div>
<div>&bull; &nbsp;Materials remain in Special Collections at all times; items do not circulate</div>
<div>&bull; &nbsp;No food or drinks are allowed in the Special Collections</div>
<div>&bull; &nbsp;Only pencils can be used for taking notes</div>
<div>&bull; &nbsp;Before making any copies, ask Reading Room staff permission</div>
<div>&bull; &nbsp;Handle materials carefully and respectfully at all times</div>
<div><span style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px; ">&nbsp;</span></div>
</div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><strong>Citing Archival Records</strong></div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a href="http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/en/access/documents/customer_service_guide_107_citing_archival_records.pdf">Use this guide for citing archival records</a>.</div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="color: rgb(88, 88, 88); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><strong>Parking</strong><br /><a href="https://brocku.ca/parking-services/">Brock University parking information</a>.</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
